    <item>
      <title>印度削减进口关税以促进本土制造业和出口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/india-cuts-import-tariffs-to-boost-local-manufacturing-exports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度将降低电子、纺织等多个行业的一系列产品的关税，以促进当地制造业的发展并创造就业机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/india-cuts-import-tariffs-to-boost-local-manufacturing-exports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 11:50:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度延长 GIFT 城市税收优惠政策以吸引新投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/india-extends-gift-city-tax-breaks-in-bid-to-lure-new-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度政府宣布了一系列新措施，以促进对古吉拉特邦国际金融科技城（GIFT 城）的投资，这是印度自由化金融市场的尝试。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/india-extends-gift-city-tax-breaks-in-bid-to-lure-new-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 11:15:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Repubblica 报道 Tamburi 正在考虑合并 Alpitour 或 IPO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/tamburi-mulling-merger-or-ipo-of-alpitour-repubblica-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《共和国报》周六报道称，Tamburi Investment Partners SpA 在增加了对 Alpitour 旅行社的股份后，正在考虑下一步行动，但并未透露其如何获得这一信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/tamburi-mulling-merger-or-ipo-of-alpitour-repubblica-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 10:12:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
